All CSS colors should use established [colors.css](mdc:src/colors.css)

  /* Chrome Colors */
  --color-chrome: #001935;
  --color-chrome-tint-dark: rgba(0, 25, 53, 0.80);
  --color-chrome-tint-light: rgba(0, 25, 53, 0.15);
  --color-chrome-tint-hover: rgba(0, 25, 53, 0.2);
  
  --color-chrome-fg: #ffffff;
  --color-chrome-fg-secondary: #99a3ae;
  --color-chrome-fg-tertiary: #667586;
  --color-chrome-border: #1a3049;

  --color-chrome-panel: #0D243F;
  --color-chrome-panel-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);

  /* Content Colors */
  --color-content: #ffffff;
  --color-content-tint-dark: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.80);
  --color-content-tint-light: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075);
  --color-content-tint-hover: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  --color-content-fg: #000000;
  --color-content-fg-secondary: #667586;
  --color-content-fg-tertiary: #99a3ae;
  --color-content-border: #e0e0e0;

  /* Accent Colors */
  --color-accent: #00b8ff;
  --color-accent-tint: #ccf1ff;
  --color-danger: #FF4930;
  --color-danger-tint: #FFE5E0;

  /* Button Colors */
  --color-button-primary-bg: #001935;
  --color-button-primary-fg: #ffffff;
  --color-button-primary-hover: #1a3049;

  --color-button-secondary-bg: var(--color-content-tint-light);
  --color-button-secondary-fg: var(--color-content-fg);
  --color-button-secondary-hover: var(--color-content-tint-hover);

  --color-button-danger-bg: var(--color-danger);
  --color-button-danger-fg: #ffffff;
  --color-button-danger-hover: #e5311a;

  --color-button-text-fg: var(--color-content-fg);
  --color-button-text-hover: var(--color-content-tint-hover);

All CSS font and type properties should use established [typography.css](mdc:src/typography.css)

